reviewText: I remember Sabrina being on tv when I was a child. I bought this for my 7 year old, and she loved it. She watched it for probably a week straight!
I purchased this DVD a little while ago and was excited for it to arrive. Sabrina the Animated Series is cute and great for the little ones! I recommend it!

With a touch of magic and a dish of chaos, Sabrina is sure to win your heart with this collection of 10 spell-binding episodes.

 Episodes Include:

1. Shrink to Fit

2. Boy Meets Bike

3. When In Rome

4. You said a Mouse-fu

5. Boogie Shoes

6. Stone Broke

7. Anywhere But Here

8. Nothin Says Lovin like Somethin from a Coven

9. Ive got Glue Babe

10. Wag the Witch

Bonus Episode from Sabrina: The Secret Life
Arrived quickly and as described .Very cute series !

Brand new in case, sticker on case read 5.99$ I believe, I payed less than that with shipping.  Very happy with shipping time, my daughter loved it also. Waiting on another Sabrina now.....will order again.
All of the children that I have shared this with have asked for more so I know that all of the Sabrina animated CDs are well worth it....I too love to watch with the children.
